wikipedia_page.main: Denis Tunnicliffe, Baron Tunnicliffe,  (born 17 January 1943) is a British pilot and railwayman. He is a Labour Life Peer, who has had several roles in the House of Lords ranging from a Government Whip to a Defence Spokesman . He is currently the Opposition Deputy Chief Whip.
